title: Wanju-Bhaku for Ladies
description:
Please note: The images are for display only. Options are available on demand as per size. We will
reach out to you with the designs options available before shipping. You can also contact us on
WhatsApp (+91629632290) if you'd like to choose beforehand. Included ~ Wanju (inner), Bakkhu (outer)
Material ~ Kuchin Quality ~ Synthetic Ready made Also commonly known as the Sherpa dress or Tibetan
dress or Bhutia dress or Chuba/ Chupa, the Kho or Bakhu is a traditional dress worn by ethnic people
of Sikkim, Nepal, Tibet. Women's Bhaku also includes a full-sleeve blouse called a honju inside the
kho; a loose gown type garment fastened near the waist, tightened with a belt. Size chart: Size
Chest size S 34"-36" M 38" L 40" XL 42" XXL 44" XXXL 46" Please note: Only exchange for Honju is
allowed post delivery.
